summary: A comprehensive fantasy style landscape overhaul for Skyrim featuring dead trees, larger trees and new forested areas.  Compatible with Enhanced Vanilla Trees and Billboards are available for use with DynDOLOD or TES5LODGen.  Updated 12/30 with improved textures for the dead snowy pines
descriptionHtml:
[center][size=6]Dark Forests of Skyrim[/size]

[size=4]by mobiusbelmont


[img]https://78.media.tumblr.com/73761eb9579b764a2152ea6f1b755cea/tumblr_ozdynq3Dvl1w7o4ndo1_1280.jpg[/img]


[/size][/center][size=4]This mod is a comprehensive, dark fantasy style, landscape overhaul for Skyrim.  The landscape will look VERY different and this mod will breathe new life to your game. 


[img]https://78.media.tumblr.com/1680f5860a67dfbf7fe60ec20f54454e/tumblr_oz7mqwWXP41s2ptqso4_540.jpg[/img]

DFOS features include over 4000 hand placed flora (trees, shrubs, mushrooms, etc), billboards for LOD generation, performance edition with low resolution textures, and a standalone version with no changes to vanilla trees

[center][youtube]ifuhG8pNKiE[/youtube]

Thanks to Jindo Skyrim for this preview with Enhanced Vanilla Trees[/center]

[center][/center]
The models used in this mod are resources from the Nexus.  Some were altered in nifskope by me to create some variety among the dead tree models available. 
[center][/center]
                       [img]https://78.media.tumblr.com/41109bd7ef32796a5e87e57c2aaa0149/tumblr_ozqj2k25tc1s2ptqso6_540.jpg[/img]

See the bottom of the page for the authors of some great resources used to make this mod.  Please consider donating to these amazing and talented artists.

 [img]https://78.media.tumblr.com/63ae43de3dd33bb769c62f1b3dca1d23/tumblr_ozqj2k25tc1s2ptqso2_540.jpg[/img]

I've been working on this mod for over a year and have completely rebuild this from scratch.  As mentioned above, a stand-alone version which does not change or edit vanilla tree models is available  


[center][/center]
[left][/left][center][/center][center][youtube]cq63Prz3x5U[/youtube][/center]
[center]Thanks to [url=https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCoEjvAplB6GaVJjCAwx3fJA]Hodilton [/url]for this preview[/center]


This mod makes the following changes:


Adds over 1000 hand placed dead pines to mountain areas, forests, and snow covered areas.  
[/size][size=5]UPDATED 12/30 with better textures thanks to [url=https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/users/13593925]Zhoulia[/url]﻿ Please drop her an endorsement[/size]
[img]https://78.media.tumblr.com/5b987c1a335b5535a5c6934af9ea5468/tumblr_ox6gwtOQiS1s2ptqso7_540.jpg[/img][img]https://78.media.tumblr.com/f1c0d8b92deddf2389f97736e540f0e2/tumblr_p1sl0gEPcL1s2ptqso1_540.jpg[/img]



[size=4]The Rift has a combination of dead and living aspen type trees, while pines in the interior have been removed.  Patches available for [url=https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/51069/?]Realistic Aspen Trees[/url], [url=https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/86077/?]The Blue Forest[/url] and [url=https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/29398/?]Aspens to Cherry Blossoms[/url], and other mods.  Ground fog has also been added to many areas of The Rift[/size]

[img]https://78.media.tumblr.com/d94fe2a18b96c4285f4167c2b5f9d027/tumblr_owx5vpfSlc1s2ptqso2_540.jpg[/img]
[img]https://78.media.tumblr.com/a64156d2d6278260181aa3d2053dec72/tumblr_ox6gwtOQiS1s2ptqso4_540.jpg[/img]

[size=4]
[/size][size=4]Eastmarch hot springs now have more dead trees, living aspens near the forest edge, more grass near Witchmist Grove, and a GIANT mushroom forest[/size]

[img]https://78.media.tumblr.com/369de5d35db60c4ef599788e72407ca0/tumblr_ox6gwtOQiS1s2ptqso1_540.jpg[/img]
[img]https://78.media.tumblr.com/5a55adbe34500e48ace5d4a11dff1b4b/tumblr_ox6i55exoi1s2ptqso4_540.jpg[/img]



[size=4]Whiterun plains are still open and grassy with living and dead trees added to areas of interest,farms, and the entire area of Rorikstead is now a living and vibrant oasis[/size]

[img]https://78.media.tumblr.com/21ffabf3f7e41d2f520b655031dc8291/tumblr_owx5vpfSlc1s2ptqso3_540.jpg[/img]
[img]https://78.media.tumblr.com/43cd253f87ab394935af918bc21ecb61/tumblr_ox9w1tWzWH1w7o4ndo1_540.jpg[/img]

[size=4]

[/size][size=4]The Reach is filled with over 20 types of dead trees, colorful aspens, twisted and tall juniper trees, and large cedar pines.  A Forest of giant redwood trees now stretches from south of Dragonbridge to the Crabber's Shanty[/size]

[img]https://78.media.tumblr.com/0c7f6bac13010399fc2cc2d7c5fcf4bb/tumblr_ouoy1x4Gjf1s2ptqso1_1280.jpg[/img][img]https://78.media.tumblr.com/230e0fc9ea1617fa6bee4fd61a58ed5f/tumblr_ovgkfw0v4Y1w7o4ndo2_540.jpg[/img]




[size=4]Haafingar has Tamu75 aspens along the waterways, more dead trees in the forest and a few unique groves of pine trees.  Hundreds of pines have been added to the forests as of v2.7
[/size]
[img]https://78.media.tumblr.com/6e22868b8433110cea7f6b04bace89b2/tumblr_ovgk1c6EWu1s2ptqso1_1280.jpg[/img]





[size=4]Hjaalmarch swamps many types of dead and petrified pine and reach trees and a few mushrooms[/size]


[img]https://78.media.tumblr.com/7a7a0335b4de02f2d0e2c369439e3caf/tumblr_ox6gwtOQiS1s2ptqso6_540.jpg[/img]
[img]https://78.media.tumblr.com/a18c0f3e797e09fc348c7d0cc3e0c284/tumblr_ox6hqljiQg1s2ptqso1_540.jpg[/img]




[size=4]Pine Forests in Falkreath and near Riverwood feature Cyrodiil type aspens, dead trees, and small juniper pines.  Hundreds of additional pines have been added as of v2.7[/size]

[img]https://78.media.tumblr.com/22e84504a72918ef3a4a0c8a4c27926c/tumblr_ox6gwtOQiS1s2ptqso3_540.jpg[/img]
[img]https://78.media.tumblr.com/42a036a22ceb18f298d2461cfb130d22/tumblr_ox9v2b44C91w7o4ndo1_540.jpg[/img]





[size=5][b]Compatibility:
[/b][/size]
[size=4]DRAGONBORN AND DAWNGUARD DLCs required!![/size]

[size=4]This mod adds thousands of hand placed trees and flora to Skyrim, and its impossible to make this compatible with every single player home or other mod which adds static objects.  if you have a tree growing through your house or town, please just delete it with the command console
[/size]

[size=4]This mod is compatible with [url=https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/47989/?]TES Legendary Cities[/url]!

This mod is compatible with [url=https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/76086/?]Enhanced Vanilla Trees[/url]! 
- I recommend using the standalone version with EVT and an aspen mod of your choice, then generate tree LOD with DynDOLOD or TES5LODGen

[/size]
[size=4]This mod is compatible with Skyrim Flora Overhaul. Install SFO first and then Dark Forests of Skyrim.  A patch for SFO and the Blue Forest is also available, as well as the core files and billboards for LOD generation.  

Compatible with Skyrim Bigger Trees and Dark Fantasy Overhaul (patches/versions with pre-generated LOD available and also via DynDOLOD or TES5LODGen)

Technically any tree or landscape overhaul with be compatible with Dark Forests if those overhauls have billboards and that you use either program above to generate LOD.  If the mods you are combining with DFOS add objects or trees you may have some clipping, that can remedied with the 'disable' feature in the command console.  
[/size]

[size=4]This mod does not add trees for worldspaces outside of tamriel.  However changes to vanilla trees will be seen so I recommend generating tree LOD for those worldspaces so the distant trees match their close up 3-D model.  Billboards without core files are available in the miscellaneous section. 

[u][b]If you are using a landscape overhaul for Solstheim or other new lands mod like Falskaar or Beyond Skyrim Bruma then you will need to generate new tree LOD for that worldspace[/b][/u].  The full version changes 10 pine tree models to dead trees, which will effect Solstheim and other mods that use these vanilla pines[/size]







[b][size=5]Installation: [/size][/b]

[size=4]Install ONLY ONE MAIN file:

Vanilla Skyrim with no other landscape overhauls

Skyrim Flora Overhaul (SFO)

SFO plus Dark Fantasy Overhaul

Core files plus Billboards: if you plan to generate your own tree LOD with TES5LODGen or DynDOLOD.  NOTE: This file does NOT contain aspen assets or billboards, install the aspen mod of your choice before generating LOD



[u][b]
Out of box OPTIONAL files available for several aspen and other tree mods.[/b][/u]  

Install one of the main files first and then install one of the optional files (these contain LOD only) for your choice of mods.   The OPTIONAL files section contains aspen tree mod patches for both vanilla Skyrim AND Skyrim Flora Overhaul
[/size][size=4]
[url=https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/51069/?]Realistic Aspen trees[/url] version: install RAT first then overwrite with this mod

[url=https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/86077/?]Blue Forest[/url] version: just install and go (works fine with or without pre-installed blue forest mod)
This will give you blue aspens in the Rift

[url=https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/29398/?]Aspens to Cherry Blossoms[/url] (ATCB) version: install lighter pink ATCB first, then this mod will give you pink aspens in The Rift

[url=https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/62849/?]Tamu75 Alternative aspen[/url] version: install Tamu75 aspen mod first and then this mod. NOTE the esp for thie mod is not needed, only the meshes and textures
[/size]

[size=4][url=https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/17168/?]Skyrim Bigger Trees[/url].  Install SBT first, then overwrite with this mod.  I HIGHLY recommend this mod, especially wiyh DynDOLOD or TES5LODGen.  ONLY the esp is needed from this mod to work with DFOS, not the loose files



[/size][size=3]REMINDER for TES5LODGen users :  If you want to combine other landscape or tree overhauls with Dark Forests, then you must have billboards for the corresponding mods.  Make sure to install the vanilla billboards first, then install all other billboards [u]IN THE SAME ORDER THAT YOU INSTALLED THE TREE MODS[/u].  Once billboards are installed, then use TES5LODGen to generate LOD for trees.  


Please see the very detailed and specific instructions for DynDOLOD on the DynDOLOD page.  

ERROR GENERATING TREE LOD?  if you are getting error messages about the tree atlas being full, you'll need to delete some billboards OR use lower resolution vanilla billboards (they are on the TES5LODGen page).  The tree atlas can only hold so many trees and not every tree will fit.  Larger size billboards (higher resolution) will take up more space too


[/size][size=4]PERFORMANCE VERSION: low resolution textures are available in archive form.  Install main or optional file first, then overwrite with the performance edition. 


STANDALONE VERSION for EVT users:  This version, in miscellaneous section, does not change any vanilla trees and is specifically for users of Enhanced Vanilla Trees and DynDOLOD.  No LOD is provided and users of the standalone must run DynDOLOD or TES5LODGen.  Billboards for a non-vanilla trees provided.  While made with EVT in mind, EVT is not necessary for the standalone version but you MUST generate your own lod



Recommended ENB presets for spooky and dark Skyrim

[/size]- any preset by [url=https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/users/10294040/?tb=mods&pUp=1]LaBeatbeatbox[/url]
- Grim and Somber ENBs
- Otherworld ENB
- Bloodborne ENB
- Dark Eden ENB
- any preset by [url=https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/users/26814739/?]ChrisKley[/url]
- Trinity ENB
- Shadow ENB
- Noir ENB




[size=3][url=https://www.tumblr.com/blog/belmontswhip]Follow me on tumblr[/url] for screenshots and updates on mods I'm working on


Changelog:

2.0: initial release

2.1: reduced size of aspens for all main files to prevent pop-in effect

2.2: optimized all textures, removed problematic larger vanilla pines/reverted to vanilla sized pines, all main files now have better tree LOD that includes the giant junipers, and giant juniper billboard added to 'core plus BB' full version

2.5: removed some floating trees (including the one above bleakwind basin), removed some billboards and LOD for problematic models, added dead juniper trees to The Reach, and added about 200 more trees to all the provinces (more coming in future updates) 

hotfix for 2.5: fixed floating mushrooms in Eastmarch hot springs


2.6:    - fixed mis-matched LOD 
    - Vurt Bent Pines and other models now have 3-D LODs
    -  fixed floatin mushrooms in Eastmarch
   - added dead junipers to the Reach
   - removed and replaced some aspen models in the Rift
   - added patch for Tamu75 Alternative Aspens


2.7: - fixed mountain blocking the entrance to Mzulft
- added patch for SFO and Dark Fantasy Overhaul
- tested LOD for all trees and replaced billboards for problematic models with CK 'full lod' option
- added over 500 vanilla pines to Falkreath and Haafingar
- added more groves of unique trees
- confirmed compatibility with Skyrim Bigger Trees and added patch for vanilla Skyrim 
- re-worked some of the textures for the 3AM dead pines and the redwoods
- added aspen tree patches for vanilla Skyrim and SFO for version 2.7
- added standalone version 2.7

UPDATE 2.7:  vastly improved dead snowy pine textures added (high and low res) by Zhoulia


Credits:
 
Tamu75 for the aspens
HiltsBrandon for Aspens to Cherry Blossoms

Vurt for some dead models, a few [url=https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/141/?]textures and the large juniper trees[/url]
3AMt for the [url=https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/61932/?]dead pines[/url]
Elenin and Ztree for their outstanding [url=https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/38651/?]tree resource[/url]
Zilav for the amazing billboard generator tool and TES5LODGen
Sheson for DynDOLOD[/size]
